{"tid":1580634,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"其實新屋嶺有冇輪姦可以咁fc","createTime":"2019-09-19T07:22:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:32:43.000Z","uid":263994,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b795b98532aebf073cc8e8ccc8e288ec6d38b852","tid":1580634,"uid":263994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:22:46.000Z","msg":"次次攞證據出嚟講都係Facebook啲status或者WhatsApp截圖<br />\n話係社工嘅一手資料<br />\nFacebook status同截圖我都識作啦<br />\n可信性太低<br />\n<br />\n如果冇被姦嘅女義士出嚟現身說法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">咁可唔可以係女義士授權社工搵民陣或者議員講啊？</span><br />\n我知若然屬實成件事係可以煲到好大<br />\n但如果冇後續證據就唔該唔好乾煲<br />\n阻住正常post上熱門<br />\n<br />\n連外國記者都提我地唔好係咁亂傳fake news <br />\n唔該唔好將自己降格做藍絲之流<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">仲有831啲通靈post都唔該收一收斂</span>"},{"pid":"94f4a6b04e71591a7884c51ff115fdab998c2917","tid":1580634,"uid":283740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"其實被自殺嘅女性，有可能係輪姦的受害人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06962b7652ac94e7977b454bfe62255658e5c3e5","tid":1580634,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:25:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2921e6e3fb1a61c543906221377a720bcd62ee2c","tid":1580634,"uid":211525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94f4a6b04e71591a7884c51ff115fdab998c2917","tid":1580634,"uid":283740,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:24:03.000Z","msg":"其實被自殺嘅女性，有可能係輪姦的受害人。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T07:26:16.000Z","msg":"黑警姦完如果唔殺，對佢地好不利，隨時搵到証據，所以正常姦完應該會殺埋"},{"pid":"a704af3658687966c2572cc7fc0b58e7b0429ec7","tid":1580634,"uid":283740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2921e6e3fb1a61c543906221377a720bcd62ee2c","tid":1580634,"uid":211525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"94f4a6b04e71591a7884c51ff115fdab998c2917","tid